      <h3 id="use_case_development_guidelines">CodeX Use Case Development Guidelines</h3>
      <p>CodeX created Use Case Development Guidelines as a framework and decision process for successful Use Case discovery, planning, development, implementation, adoption, and impact. The CodeX Execution stage will be covered in the <%= link_to("Implementation & Testing","implementation.html") %> and <%= link_to("Adoption & Value","adoption.html")%> sections.</p>
